cleaned_text: Gwen Casten, age 17, second from left. She was vaccinated and died in her sleep. Young kids don’t die in their sleep. It is very very rare. But it’s the new normal after the COVID vaccines rolled out. These deaths are only happening to kids vaccinated with the COVID vaccines. …
